      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, complete with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and the factory M Variable Differential Lock. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a VANOS service and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the chassis handles the torque loads with precision. The suspension maintains its original geometry, providing the communicative steering and balanced turn-in characteristic of this platform. While it shows the honest patina of a car that has been enjoyed, its performance envelope remains sharp and visceral. A purist-spec build for the serious driver.",
